          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets used for all isotopes were over 98% pure,",
                "metallic, self-supporting foils of 2cm x 1cm.",
                "A metallic foil of only 12 mg/cm2 (120 keV) was",
                "magnesium work, therefore a 85 mg/cm2 foil of",
                "magnesium oxide used at large angles to give",
                "reasonable counting rates. This was feasible",
                "above where the oxygen peak was well separated",
                "from the inelastic magnesium peak owing to the",
                "kinematics of the reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
